.\docs\guide\getting-started.md:14:DINOForge requires the **modified BepInEx 5 with Unity ECS support** from Nexus Mods. Standard BepInEx from GitHub will **not** work — this game requires a custom-forked `winhttp.dll` (Doorstop) that enables loading multiple assemblies from the `ecs_plugins/` directory, which is how Unity ECS plugins are bootstrapped. The fork was created by devopsdinosaur specifically for this game.
